{"tid":617912,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] King’s Raid #105 繼續養生","createTime":"2018-04-05T11:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T14:47:11.000Z","uid":71021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd57a41e00dd047bf428324ab903e8551c33d66","tid":617912,"uid":71021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Server【Japan】</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/141711_dedcc7b9deea6af5d8691a925b55be6f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F141711_dedcc7b9deea6af5d8691a925b55be6f.png&h=72e0e3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻煩新手巴絲睇咗全攻略先，睇完有咩唔明再問，所有攻略僅供參考</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【LIHKG】King's Raid 全攻略</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>【日服連登公會】 </strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>新手巴絲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span></span>亂入公會，要入就入Lihkg公會<br />\n因為你一入錯，要退會入Lihkg公會，就要等足七日先會有奬勵你拎<br />\n唔使問有無位，搵到即係有，搵唔到即係無<br />\n申請咗邊個公會+ID麻煩填表，優先處理填表巴絲<br />\n填完麻煩再係Post度留名話自己填咗表，即有專人為你服務</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只限日服適用 - 刷首抽Q&amp;A</strong></span></span><br />\n所有Q&amp;A僅供參考，各巴絲可自行選擇有愛之英雄作為目標<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：點解我無得抽嘅？</span><br />\nA：麻煩出Game再入Game睇下自己揀咗咩Ser，目前只有日服先會有得刷廿抽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：點樣拎廿抽？</span><br />\nA：打完頭三關教學任務，去右上角信箱拎石同十抽卷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：抽邊個Pool好？點解？</span><br />\nA：首推刺客Pool<br />\n因為每隻英都會有個人專用嘅<br />\nUW = Unique Weapon <br />\nUT = Unique Treasure<br />\n兩樣係唔同嘅裝備，裝嘅位置唔一樣，可以同時使用，將隻英發揮到最大嘅效果<br />\n因為有52隻英，咁就唔一一貼上嚟<br />\n<br />\n全英雄Skill、UT、UW、Artifact整合英文版：<br />\n<a href=\"https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com/?item=Kasel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaskofgoblin.netlify.com%2F%3Fitem%3DKasel&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=61ae28cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com/?item=Kasel</a><br />\n<br />\n全英雄Skill、UW整合殘體中文版：(非最新版本，所以麻煩連埋第一頁全攻略嚟睇)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067&amp;rand=824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.ngacn.cc%2Fread.php%3Ftid%3D12943067%26rand%3D824&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=199dec50\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067&amp;rand=824</a><br />\n<br />\n全英雄UT殘體中文版：(如果唔知佢講啲英係邊隻去上面全人物圖鑑對/直接問)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=13705992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.ngacn.cc%2Fread.php%3Ftid%3D13705992&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=b53ef736\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=13705992</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">刺客Pool原因：</span><br />\n入面有幾把unique weapon(uw) 同unique treasure(ut)都比較勁<br />\n不過最重要係有愛&gt;一切，抽其他pool都得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：抽到咩先開局？</span><br />\nA:如果你係跟大圍抽刺客Pool的話<br />\n抽中Mirianne既UW/UT，Roi既UW/UT，Epis既UW/UT，都推介大家開局<br />\n同埋建議係UT&gt;UW，因為UW 15日會送自選劵，但UT暫時係無劵可以自選，最多隨機<br />\n但52隻英幾時先會中到你想要嗰隻...<br />\n如果巴絲唔肯定開局與否請上嚟問我哋<br />\n都係嗰句，有愛就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：如何刪帳重刷？</span><br />\nA：1：撳左上角個頭像<br />\n2：Others<br />\n3：Leave<br />\n4：之後打句【I agree to delete my account】就搞掂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/200034_a35f6a580aa96407913fd1a390b58af5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F200034_a35f6a580aa96407913fd1a390b58af5.jpg&h=421ef0e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">謹記<br />\n將方法將會刪除帳號內資料<br />\n所以真係棄先好打</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家刷到好開局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"8c80947b0eeabeb5b09a9f57d60c52ed2c9a9e18","tid":617912,"uid":67317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T11:54:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/617909/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/617909/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d15223f5771dc51d5f95e75440f56d9c8783d047","tid":617912,"uid":23470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"想問下大佬們點睇新女盾?"}]}